AsymmetricDecrypt.title: AsymmetricDecrypt
AsymmetricDecrypt.summary: Decrypts data by using an asymmetric key.

AsymmetricEncrypt.title: AsymmetricEncrypt
AsymmetricEncrypt.summary: Encrypts data by using an asymmetric customer master key (CMK).

AsymmetricSign.title: AsymmetricSign
AsymmetricSign.summary: Generates a signature by using an asymmetric key.

AsymmetricVerify.title: AsymmetricVerify
AsymmetricVerify.summary: Verifies a signature by using an asymmetric key.

CancelKeyDeletion.title: CancelKeyDeletion
CancelKeyDeletion.summary: Cancels the deletion task of a CMK.

CertificatePrivateKeyDecrypt.title: CertificatePrivateKeyDecrypt
CertificatePrivateKeyDecrypt.summary: Decrypts data by using a specific certificate.

CertificatePrivateKeySign.title: CertificatePrivateKeySign
CertificatePrivateKeySign.summary: Generates a signature by using a specified certificate.

CertificatePublicKeyEncrypt.title: CertificatePublicKeyEncrypt
CertificatePublicKeyEncrypt.summary: Encrypts data by using a specific certificate.

CertificatePublicKeyVerify.title: CertificatePublicKeyVerify
CertificatePublicKeyVerify.summary: Verifies a digital signature by using a specified certificate.

CreateAlias.title: CreateAlias
CreateAlias.summary: Creates an alias for a customer master key (CMK).

CreateKeyVersion.title: CreateKeyVersion
CreateKeyVersion.summary: Creates a version for a customer master key (CMK).

CreateSecret.title: CreateSecret
CreateSecret.summary: Creates a secret and stores the initial version of the secret.

Decrypt.title: Decrypt
Decrypt.summary: Decrypts the ciphertext that is specified by the CiphertextBlob parameter.

DeleteCertificate.title: DeleteCertificate
DeleteCertificate.summary: Deletes a certificate and its private key and certificate chain.

DeleteKeyMaterial.title: DeleteKeyMaterial
DeleteKeyMaterial.summary: Deletes the key material that you imported.

DescribeAccountKmsStatus.title: DescribeAccountKmsStatus
DescribeAccountKmsStatus.summary: Queries the status of Key Management Service (KMS) within your Alibaba Cloud account.

DescribeKey.title: DescribeKey
DescribeKey.summary: Queries the information about a customer master key (CMK).

DescribeKeyVersion.title: DescribeKeyVersion
DescribeKeyVersion.summary: Queries detailed information about a specified customer master key (CMK) version.

DescribeSecret.title: DescribeSecret
DescribeSecret.summary: Queries the metadata of a secret.

EnableKey.title: EnableKey
EnableKey.summary: Enables a customer master key (CMK) to encrypt and decrypt data.

Encrypt.title: Encrypt
Encrypt.summary: Encrypts plaintext by using a symmetric CMK.

ExportDataKey.title: ExportDataKey
ExportDataKey.summary: Encrypts a data key by using a specific public key and exports the data key.

GenerateAndExportDataKey.title: GenerateAndExportDataKey
GenerateAndExportDataKey.summary: Randomly generates a data key and uses a CMK and a public key to encrypt the data key. This operation returns both the ciphertext of the data key encrypted by using the CMK and that encrypted by using the public key.

GenerateDataKey.title: GenerateDataKey
GenerateDataKey.summary: Generates a random data key that is used to locally encrypt data.

GenerateDataKeyWithoutPlaintext.title: GenerateDataKeyWithoutPlaintext
GenerateDataKeyWithoutPlaintext.summary: Generates a random data key, which can be used to encrypt local data.

GetCertificate.title: GetCertificate
GetCertificate.summary: Queries a certificate that is managed by Certificates Manager.

GetParametersForImport.title: GetParametersForImport
GetParametersForImport.summary: Queries the parameters that are used to import key material for a customer master key (CMK).

GetPublicKey.title: GetPublicKey
GetPublicKey.summary: Obtains the public key of an asymmetric key pair. You can use the public key to encrypt local data and verify signatures.

ImportKeyMaterial.title: ImportKeyMaterial
ImportKeyMaterial.summary: Call the ImportKeyMaterial operation to import the key material.

ListAliases.title: ListAliases
ListAliases.summary: Queries all aliases in the current region for the current account.

ListAliasesByKeyId.title: ListAliasesByKeyId
ListAliasesByKeyId.summary: Queries all aliases that are bound to a specified customer master key (CMK).

ListKeyVersions.title: ListKeyVersions
ListKeyVersions.summary: Queries all versions of a specified CMK.

ListKeys.title: ListKeys
ListKeys.summary: Queries all customer master keys (CMKs) of the current Alibaba Cloud account in the current region.

ListResourceTags.title: ListResourceTags
ListResourceTags.summary: Queries the tags of a customer master key (CMK).

ListSecretVersionIds.title: ListSecretVersionIds
ListSecretVersionIds.summary: Queries all versions of a secret.

ListSecrets.title: ListSecrets
ListSecrets.summary: Queries all secrets created by the current Alibaba Cloud account in the current region.

OpenKmsService.title: OpenKmsService
OpenKmsService.summary: Activates Key Management Service (KMS) under your Alibaba cloud account.

PutSecretValue.title: PutSecretValue
PutSecretValue.summary: Stores the secret value of a new version into a secret.

ReEncrypt.title: ReEncrypt
ReEncrypt.summary: Re-encrypts ciphertext. When you call this operation, KMS first decrypts the specified ciphertext and then uses a different CMK to encrypt the obtained plaintext data or data key and return ciphertext.

ScheduleKeyDeletion.title: ScheduleKeyDeletion
ScheduleKeyDeletion.summary: Deletes a specified customer master key (CMK).

SetDeletionProtection.title: SetDeletionProtection
SetDeletionProtection.summary: Enables or disables deletion protection for a customer master key (CMK).

TagResource.title: TagResource
TagResource.summary: Adds tags to a customer master key (CMK), secret, or certificate.

UntagResource.title: UntagResource
UntagResource.summary: Removes tags from a customer master key (CMK), secret, or certificate.

UpdateAlias.title: UpdateAlias
UpdateAlias.summary: Binds an existing alias to a different customer master key (CMK) ID.

UpdateCertificateStatus.title: UpdateCertificateStatus
UpdateCertificateStatus.summary: Updates the status of a certificate.

UpdateKeyDescription.title: UpdateKeyDescription
UpdateKeyDescription.summary: Updates the description of a CMK.

UpdateSecret.title: UpdateSecret
UpdateSecret.summary: Updates the metadata of a secret.

UpdateSecretRotationPolicy.title: UpdateSecretRotationPolicy
UpdateSecretRotationPolicy.summary: Updates the rotation policy of a secret.

UpdateSecretVersionStage.title: UpdateSecretVersionStage
UpdateSecretVersionStage.summary: Updates the stage label that marks a secret version.

UploadCertificate.title: UploadCertificate
UploadCertificate.summary: Imports a certificate and a certificate chain issued by a certificate authority (CA) into Certificates Manager.
